title: Euler.Lettre.Digital to be released
text:
The digital platform Opera-Bernoulli-Euler will be inaugurated on Saturday 24 February at 12h00. You find the website at this link.It will commence with the publication of all volumes of Euler Opera Omnia and search functionality. The platform will be continuously enhanced with the latest AI functionality from Lettre AI. It will be open to contributions from the community and will include updates from the publications of the Bernoulli Euler Kommission. Interested in the project? You can subscribe to the newsletter to receive the latest news and updates.
